# Bearer token for bridge auth. Set this to the same value as your Gizmo
# AI Gateway token (cf_api_token) — single Keychain entry, two header
# names. Or generate a fresh random value: openssl rand -hex 32.
#
# This file is parsed by Cloudflare's Deploy-to-Cloudflare wizard to
# present a SANDBOX_API_KEY input field during deployment. See:
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/changelog/post/2025-07-01-workers-deploy-button-supports-environment-variables-and-secrets/
SANDBOX_API_KEY=
